OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FThis report by ITV News Correspondent
OL,8,FSejal Karia contains details you may
OL,9,Ffind distressing
OL,11,FAdditional reporting by ITV Senior
OL,12,FProducers Eleanor Gregory and Louisa
OL,13,FFelton
OL,15,FFor years, 'Lucy' had endured years of
OL,16,Fabuse at the hands of her husband.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
