PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,F"A night or two before our wedding, he
OL,8,Fpunched me by the front door, so I had
OL,9,Fto put a lot of our wedding photos in
OL,10,Fblack and white so the bruises
OL,11,Fwouldn't show".
OL,13,FBut nothing prepared her what she
OL,14,Fdiscovered one night in late 2021.
OL,26,@sD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,F"I woke to a stranger on top of me
OL,8,Fraping me and my husband in the room
OL,9,Fwatching over. The stranger got up and
OL,10,Fran off quite quickly, and then I
OL,11,Fbarricaded myself in my children's
OL,12,Froom and called my father...and called
OL,13,Fthe police."
OL,15,FHe confessed that he'd invited
OL,16,Fstrangers into their family home to
OL,17,Fabuse her. Men who are still free.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,F"I said, what have you have you done?
OL,8,FAnd he said, I have to go inside or
OL,9,FI'm going to end up killing you. And I
OL,10,Fsaid, what do you mean? He said, this
OL,11,Fhas happened eight more times. This
OL,12,Fisn't the first time."
OL,14,F"I spend every day of my life in fear
OL,15,Fand worry. But more than that, I feel
OL,16,Fupset that these men are walking free."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
