PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FLucy said that she doesn't know who
OL,8,Fher perpetrators are. She said, "They
OL,9,Fprobably think that they've completely
OL,10,Fgot away with the crimes that they've
OL,11,Fdone and therefore may even be
OL,12,Fcontinuing."
OL,14,FAbuse that was happening in her home
OL,15,Fand in her own bed while her children
OL,16,Fslept in their bedrooms just feet
OL,17,Faway. She was being drugged so heavily
OL,18,Fwith sleeping medication and
OL,19,Feventually car cleaning fluid, she had
OL,20,Fno idea what was happening.
OL,26,@pD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,F"The police came and me and my mother
OL,8,Fwere sat there and they told me that
OL,9,Fhe had been drugging me. I felt I'd
OL,10,Fbeen shot in the stomach. It was such
OL,11,Fa shock.
OL,13,F"Then they told me what he was
OL,14,Fdrugging me with, which was car
OL,15,Fcleaner. I think the first thing that
OL,16,FI find shocking and upsetting is the
OL,17,Ffact that when it was delivered, I
OL,18,Fopened the package and he told me he
OL,19,Fjust needed it for the car."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FThe first time he drugged her, she
OL,8,Fsays, he later told her he thought he
OL,9,Fhad killed her.
OL,11,F"He stood over my body for half an
OL,12,Fhour and he didn't call anybody."
OL,14,F"I would wake up and things would hurt
OL,15,Fin my body and I wondered whyI became
OL,16,Fso unwell for years. I look back at
OL,17,Fphotos (and) I don't even recognise
OL,18,Fmyself."
OL,26,@yD@HpmyD@Lpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
