OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FLucy told us how she put her symptoms
OL,8,Fdown to just being unwell as she
OL,9,Fcouldn't find any answers for them at
OL,10,Fthe time.
OL,12,F"I started wetting the bed and I
OL,13,Fhadn't even wet the bed as a child. I
OL,14,Fwouldn't be able to sit up and sip
OL,15,Fwater...and I remember one night I
OL,16,Fsaid to him, I think I'm going to die
OL,17,Ftonight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,F"Will you watch me as I sleep? And he
OL,8,Fsaid 'yes'. And then when he called me
OL,9,Ffrom prison he told me that he got me
OL,10,Fraped that night."
OL,12,FHer ex-partner was eventually jailed
OL,13,Fand is currently serving his sentence,
OL,14,Fwith the other men that he invited to
OL,15,Frape his wife at home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
