PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FLucy says police failed to properly
OL,8,Finvestigate the other men her ex-
OL,9,Fpartner said were involved. She says
OL,10,Fyears were lost and opportunities to
OL,11,Fgather evidence were missed making her
OL,12,Ffeel "totally let-down".
OL,14,F"Despite the fact the police were
OL,15,Faware that a stranger had been in my
OL,16,Fhome that night and admitted to other
OL,17,Fmen being in our property to rape me
OL,18,Fpreviously, they didn't fingerprint
OL,19,Fthe bed frame," she says.
OL,26,@tD@FOUtD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FShe kept the bed frame for years, even
OL,8,Fmoving house with it. Police later
OL,9,Fidentified DNA from multiple
OL,10,Findividuals. Some profiles remain
OL,11,Funmatched. None of the men have been
OL,12,Fcaught.
OL,14,FDespite now having confidence that the
OL,15,Fpolice have cared about the case, she
OL,16,Fsaid that a specialist operation
OL,17,Fshould have been put in place in the
OL,18,Ffirst place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
