PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FDetermined to find answers, she began
OL,8,Finvestigating herself. Recovering
OL,9,Femails, tracing online accounts and
OL,10,Fpreserving evidence.
OL,12,FWhat she uncovered, she believes,
OL,13,Fsuggests the abuse may have been
OL,14,Fhappening for many years and may have
OL,15,Finvolved many more men.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,F"He said he was drugging me two to
OL,8,Fthree times a week for a
OL,9,Fyear...evidence from emails and so
OL,10,Fforth shows that it was going on for
OL,11,Fmany many years prior if you times two
OL,12,For three times a week across many
OL,13,Fyears, it could be hundreds."
OL,15,FEven after he was jailed, her ex-
OL,16,Fpartner continued contacting her
OL,17,Fthrough letters from prison, artwork
OL,18,Fand gifts ` even calling her from jail.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
