SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FIn recorded prison conversations,
OL,8,Fobtained by ITV News, her ex-partner
OL,9,Fadmitted to drugging her and inviting
OL,10,Fother men into the family home to
OL,11,Fabuse her while she lay unconscious.
OL,13,FIn one letter from prison, he wrote
OL,14,F"the real me accepts me for the
OL,15,Fmonster that I am".
OL,17,FLucy believes, her ex-partner should
OL,18,Fnever have been allowed to contact her
OL,19,Ffrom prison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
