PN,31115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FBut as it stands, the men are still at
OL,8,Flarge and for Lucy, the fear has never
OL,9,Fgone away.
OL,11,F"Everyday I walk past people and
OL,12,Fwonder if someone looks at me for too
OL,13,Flong, I'm concerned, maybe that's one
OL,14,Fof them."
OL,16,F"I'd been scared of walking in the
OL,17,Fdark outside for so many years of my
OL,18,Flife. But actually I needed to be
OL,19,Ffearful of being in my own home and in
OL,20,Fmy own bed."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
