PN,31116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FAs a survivor of sexual abuse, Lucy is
OL,8,Fprotected by anonymity but has
OL,9,Fpartially waived this right as she
OL,10,Fwants to share her story with ITV News
OL,11,Fto let women know who have gone
OL,12,Fthrough this kind of abuse that they
OL,13,Fare not alone.
OL,15,FThe force in her case - who we are not
OL,16,Fnaming to help protect Lucy's identity
OL,17,F- has told us that policing has
OL,18,Fundergone a "transformational change
OL,19,Fto the way rape investigations are
OL,20,Fcarried out through the rollout of
OL,21,Fnational programme Operation Soteria".
OL,26,@zD@MOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FThey have added that their
OL,8,Finvestigations into rape and serious
OL,9,Fsexual offences are "firmly rooted in
OL,10,Fan evidence-based approach" and that
OL,11,F"the perpetrators of rape and serious
OL,12,Fsexual offences are placed at the
OL,13,Fheart of our investigations".
OL,15,FIn response to Lucy's case, the police
OL,16,Fforce told ITV News that they are
OL,17,Fsorry that she feels let down.
OL,26,@qD@UOUrD@[O]sD@AOUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/24
