PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FThey added: "One man has received a
OL,8,Fsignificant prison sentence for the
OL,9,Fcrimes he committed against this
OL,10,Fvictim, but our enquiries are
OL,11,Fcontinuing and we remain committed to
OL,12,Fdoing all we can to identify any other
OL,13,Fperpetrators who carried out offences
OL,14,Fagainst her."
