OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FSince our last report looking at women
OL,8,Fwho have been subject to drug
OL,9,Ffacilitated sexual assault by their
OL,10,Fpartners, with Zoe Watts and Amanda
OL,11,FStanhope, who spoke to us about the
OL,12,Fabuse they experienced while
OL,13,Funconscious at the hands of former
OL,14,Fpartners, women like Zoe, Amanda and
OL,15,F'Lucy' have shared their horrendous
OL,16,Fordeals with us.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31120
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FPushing for change to support these
OL,8,Fwomen, Zoe and Amanda have together
OL,9,Fgiven evidence to a Parliamentary
OL,10,Fhearing that was chaired by Baroness
OL,11,FKennedy, a leading advocate for
OL,12,Fwomen's rights.
OL,14,FThe session addressed the systemic
OL,15,Fissues around drug facilitated sexual
OL,16,Fabuse in light of Zoe and Amanda's
OL,17,Fpersonal experiences and their
OL,18,Frecently launched campaign called
OL,19,F_EndEyeCheck.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31121
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781779674
OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,F_EndEyeCheck is a survivor-led
OL,8,Fcampaign calling for stronger
OL,9,Flegislation around the creation and
OL,10,Fsharing of abuse material linked to
OL,11,Fdrug-facilitated sexual violence with
OL,12,Fan aim to awareness of the online
OL,13,Fspaces where this abuse is normalised,
OL,14,Fshared and encouraged.
OL,16,FOn Saturday survivors marched march to
OL,17,FParliament to call on the government
OL,18,Fto open up an inquiry into how police
OL,19,Fand prosecutors deal with drug-
OL,20,Ffacilitated rape.
