OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FZoe told ITV News that the law "isn't
OL,8,Freally tackling the systematic abuse
OL,9,Fand the vulnerability of your partner"
OL,10,Fwhen women are drugged and raped
OL,11,Fwhilst unconscious.
OL,13,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,14,FNews on drug facilitated rape, the
OL,15,FDomestic Abuse Commissioner, Nicole
OL,16,FJacobs, said that this is the new face
OL,17,Fof domestic abuse and that systemic
OL,18,Fchanges are needed.
