OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,FHer calls are for the government to
OL,8,Furgently shut down online spaces where
OL,9,Fperpetrators are facilitating this
OL,10,Fkind of abuse and that there needs to
OL,11,Fbe more help for services that victims
OL,12,Fgo to for support.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News, the Domestic
OL,15,FAbuse Commissioner said: "Perpetrators
OL,16,Fof domestic abuse are going to online
OL,17,Fspaces to look for advice about how
OL,18,Fthey can facilitate and abuse
OL,19,Feffectively without any kind of
OL,20,Frepercussions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/24
