OL,3,CThe woman searching for the men
OL,4,Cinvited by her husband to abuse her as
OL,5,Cshe slept
OL,7,F"And the government has a
OL,8,Fresponsibility and should be looking
OL,9,Fat these spaces, these unregulated
OL,10,Fspaces where this is happening and
OL,11,Fshut them down."
OL,13,FThe National Crime Agency have also
OL,14,Fsaid that they recognise there is a
OL,15,Fneed to urgently to respond to the
OL,16,Fabhorrent behaviours to drug
OL,17,Ffacilitated sexual abuse.
OL,19,FIf you, or someone you know, has been
OL,20,Fa victim of rape of sexual violence,
OL,21,Fthere is support out there to help:
